TV Remote Control - Smart TV is the best free iPhone/iPod remote control unit for Streaming Player and Smart TV. Magnificent design, intuitive interface, no pileup of buttons or complex settings. Thanks to this iOS application, access to movies, music and games will become simpler and easier, and you will love your TV even more. All you need is connect your iOS device and Smart TV to the same Wi-Fi network.

